overview: A wild and strange collection of raw uninhibited uncut skits, sketches and spoofs that make fun of the world wide web. Everything from commercials to movies to series to the news are spoofed. Directed by Nicholas M. Garofolo	Writing Credits Nicholas M. Garofolo, Ethan Pierce, Efrem Saliu, Maurice Tillmon, Thon Vaultron.
tagline: A wild and strange collection of raw uninhibited uncut skits, sketches and spoofs that make fun of the world wide web
title: Surfing the Web
